author: Elv1s
title: Good, But Expensive
review: Don't get me wrong, I like this set, but it was so expensive and exclusive for 40-60 parts that you can find in a classic set. Just like the other two sets, this is the 60 years anniversary edition that is set exclusively for Wal-Mart that you can buy online. Sadly, you can't buy this anymore because it is a limited edition set too. It is a good set, just too expensive.
